@startuml seq-07-collect
' 序列图7：收藏文章
title 收藏文章序列图

actor 用户 as User
participant "article-detail.js" as Front
participant "CollectController" as Ctrl
participant "CollectService" as Svc
participant "CollectMapper" as Mapper
database "MySQL" as DB

User -> Front: 点击收藏按钮
Front -> Ctrl: POST /api/article/{id}/collect
Ctrl -> Svc: toggleCollect(userId,target_type=1,target_id)
Svc -> Mapper: select(userId,target_type,target_id)
Mapper -> DB: SELECT * FROM collect_record WHERE...
DB --> Mapper: 记录(无)
Mapper --> Svc: null
Svc -> Mapper: insert(userId,target_type,target_id)
Mapper -> DB: INSERT INTO collect_record
Svc -> Mapper: updateArticleCollectCount(id,+1)
Mapper -> DB: UPDATE article SET collect_count=collect_count+1
Svc --> Ctrl: 已收藏
Ctrl --> Front: {code:200, collected:true}
Front -> Front: 更新收藏数+1,按钮变色
Front --> User: 显示已收藏状态

@enduml
